I just got back from an incredible winter road trip through the Dolomites! I took the new Audi S6 Avant e-tron on the journey, and it handled the mountain roads like a dream. 

The range was exceptional. I barely had to think about charging, which meant more time for exploring. And the lighting technology? 

It made those pre-dawn drives to sunrise hikes feel like something out of a sci-fi movie. I spent my days snowshoe hiking through fresh powder, chasing the first light on jagged peaks, and ending it all in a sauna at the top of a mountain (because why not?).

The Dolomites in winter are pure magic, and this trip was one for the books. #A6etron
